Privacy PolicyEffective Date: May 16, 2026SolSplitter (also known as SolSplit) is a simple split-screen launcher for Android devices, particularly optimized for the Solana Seeker.

1. Information We CollectWe collect no personal information.The app does not require accounts, login, or any user registration.
All data (saved app pairs) is stored locally on your device only.
We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal data, device identifiers, location, or usage analytics.

2. PermissionsSolSplitter / SolSplit requires the following standard Android permissions:Query installed apps – To show you the list of apps you can launch.
Launch other apps – To open apps in split-screen mode.

No other permissions are requested.

3. Data SharingWe do not share any data with third parties.
The app does not contain any analytics, advertising, or tracking SDKs.

4. Local StorageSaved app pairs are stored locally using Android’s SharedPreferences. You can clear this data anytime through your device settings.

5. Children’s PrivacyThis app is not directed at children under 13 and does not knowingly collect data from children.

6. Changes to This PolicyWe may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Any changes will be posted in this repository.

